.DT
mend
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
mend

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
mend - Stitch up clothing.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
mend <item> with <object>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command allows you to stitch up damaged clothes with a needle and thread.
You need to be holding a threaded needle to use this command.  If your bonus
in crafts.materials.sewing is high enough for the job, you may be able to
mend the item completely; otherwise you will only be able to mend it a little
at a time.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> mend sweater with needle
You carefully stitch up all the holes in the angora sweater.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
leatherwork, fix
.EP
